title: Did the controversial jacket of Milania Trump contain a message in favour of fascism?
subtitle: Some elements of the viral publication about the Melania Trump jacket are factual, but there is no evidence that they refer to the fascist slogan "I'm Ne Frigo."
author: Kim LaCapria
vclaim: Melania Trump made a malicious reference to Mer Mussolini's motto, "I don't really care about Yu." A jacket.
